{
  "id" : 736,
  "songNumber" : 124,
  "title" : "SWEET HOUR OF PRAYER",
  "language" : "english",
  "originalKey" : "D",
  "capo" : 0,
  "bpm" : 0,
  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Sweet hour of prayer, sweet hour of prayer,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 28
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "That calls me from a world of care,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And bids me, at my Father's throne,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Make all my wants and wishes known;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In seasons of distress and grief,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "My soul has often found relief,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And oft escaped the tempter's snare,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "By thy return, sweet hour of prayer.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 29
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Sweet hour of prayer, sweet hour of prayer,"
    }, {
      "text" : "The joy I feel, the bliss I share,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Of those whose anxious spirits burn",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 23
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "With strong desires for thy return !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 24
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "With such I hasten to the place",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Where God, my Saviour, shows His face,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And gladly take my station there,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And wait for thee, sweet hour of prayer.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 25
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Sweet hour of prayer, sweet hour of prayer,"
    }, {
      "text" : "Thy wings shall my petition bear",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 23
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "To Him whose truth and faithfulness",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 23
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Engage the waiting soul to bless;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And since He bids me seek His face,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Believe His Word and trust His grace,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I'll cast on Him my every care,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And wait for thee, sweet hour of prayer."
    } ]
  } ]
}